### **4. 29_StreamChartDisplay**  
**Description:**  
Plots a real-time line graph from numeric input data using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamChartDisplay - Live Data Plotter

StreamChartDisplay turns numeric data streams into smooth real-time line plots for visual monitoring.

## Features
- Animated Matplotlib chart  
- Scrollable x-axis  
- Works with custom or random input  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/29_StreamChartDisplay.git
cd 29_StreamChartDisplay
python visualize.py
